  "prompt": "Where are the products of Coca-Cola manufactured?",
  "response": "Coca-Cola products are manufactured in various locations around the world. The company operates a vast network of bottling plants and facilities that are strategically located to serve different markets. The primary manufacturing locations include:\n\n1. **United States**: Coca-Cola has several bottling plants across the U.S. that produce various beverages.\n\n2. **International Bottling Partners**: Coca-Cola partners with multiple bottling companies globally, which operate their own manufacturing facilities. This includes regions in Europe, Asia, Africa, Latin America, and Canada.\n\n3. **Local Facilities**: Many countries have local Coca-Cola production facilities that produce drinks tailored to regional tastes and preferences.\n\nIn addition to company-owned plants, Coca-Cola often works with independent bottlers who manufacture and distribute its products, allowing for a more efficient supply chain across different markets. The exact locations can vary based on demand and local market conditions.",
